title: Rust experimental DB60 v1261 X64 (Fixed crack) Hygaming

Rust experimental DB60 v1261 (Fixed crack)

How to run:
-Extract the zip
-Edit LumaEmu.ini to change user name. 
-Run RustClient.exe
-Press F1 and use the command: client.connect rust.hygaming.org:28015
